container size ----xtra small if the screen width is less than 576px
  ---smAll(sm) if minimum device width is 576 and  less than 768px.
  ---md : >768 and <900
  ----large(lg) if the size of screen >900 and <1200
  ---xl : if the screen width is greater than  equal to 1200
  
  
  for the input controls we will use form-control class
  
  form-label,form-control-button,dreopdown,textbox

  
  offset-md-3 : it will leave 2 label margins then will type
  
  for buttons we use class
  btn btn-primary-blue,danger-red,success-green,danger,info
  
  
